        public static BrowserId of(String json)
        Create BrowserId object from success or failure JSON response
        Parameters:
        json - the response returned by https://browserid.org
        Returns:
        a BrowserId instance with status OK if the authentication passed, or with status FAIL if the authentication failed, or null if the passed JSON response is invalid
